data.description: DIY lovers, REJOICE! This hidden gem awaits you. Take advantage of the affordable price and unique opportunity to add your personal touches and modern updates to make this house a home that you will be proud of. With a full finished basement of over 800 square feet of additional living space PLUS a cozy fireplace, a backyard perfect for entertaining, a peaceful sun room with plenty of natural light and so much more, you will never want to leave. Ample space for everyone, this home has everything you need to make memories that will last a lifetime. Home has been well-maintained with newer Pella windows and patio sliders, a seven-years young timberline roof, a five-year old HVAC, recently replaced Trex deck and above ground pool. A MUST see!  Schedule an appointment TODAY!
